                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #1a2980; margin-bottom: 10px;">Calculation Method</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555;">
                        VR speed calculation is based on:
                        <br>1. Base VR speed for each model at MTOW
                        <br>2. Flap setting correction (higher flaps = lower VR)
                        <br>3. Wind correction (headwind reduces VR, tailwind increases VR)
                        <br>4. Assumes standard atmospheric conditions and dry runway
                    </p>
                </div>
